{"tid":2159953,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【堅離地傾．沈旭暉 026】 楊天命（上）：「黃色風水師」的個人犧牲","createTime":"2020-08-16T15:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T15:52:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2dfb2076f51b95db3b33c3145e73ff57ba3356","tid":2159953,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:52:06.000Z","msg":"【堅離地傾．沈旭暉 026】<br />\n楊天命（上）：「黃色風水師」的個人犧牲<br />\nAug 15, 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/01RcWEFsunY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F01RcWEFsunY&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=5b00da44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/01RcWEFsunY</a><br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n148K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n風水師楊天命師傅成名於八、九十年代，六四後因為不滿北京處理手法而移居溫哥華，九七後回流香港，直到2019年的反送中運動，再次激起他的政治覺醒，除了多次表態、到抗爭現場當司機，還寫了公開信給習近平，以玄學角度剖析林鄭月娥如何禍國殃民。連番態度，讓他不時收到恐嚇電話、被藍絲抹黑為神棍，自言也不敢回內地、否則肯定被嫖娼，犧牲的生意非常多。究竟他的理念從何而來？未來又如何為自己趨吉避凶？<br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=1300a634\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsimon.diplo...&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=88a14395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...</a><br />\nPatreon: <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/simonshen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fsimonshen&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=52d4b2cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/simonshen</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/simonshen_glos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%